OL,3,CEx-pro Stewart: 'I can't tie my
OL,4,Cshoelaces any more'
OL,6,F"I live a good life, but I don't think
OL,7,FI live a normal one," he told ITV News
OL,8,Fahead of a walk between 17 stadiums to
OL,9,Fraise money for research.
OL,11,F"I love playing golf, I can't play. I
OL,12,Fcan't do my shoelaces up. I can do my
OL,13,Fbuttons up but it takes ages.
OL,15,F"I can pick things up with my right
OL,16,Fhand and I can hug things with this
OL,17,F(left) arm but I can't pick something
OL,18,Fup."
