OL,6,FDuring a career spanning 20 years,
OL,7,FStewart scored 58 goals in 133 games
OL,8,Ffor Huddersfield before leaving for
OL,9,FIpswich Town, where he became the
OL,10,FPremier League's second top scorer
OL,11,Fwith 19 goals in the 2000-01 season.
OL,13,FHe said he first noticed a change in
OL,14,Fhis health when he struggled to use
OL,15,Fhis left arm while exercising during
OL,16,Flockdown, prompting a trip to see a
OL,17,Fneurologist.
