OL,6,F"I was as shocked as anyone would be
OL,7,Fbecause I didn't expect that to
OL,8,Fhappen, or I didn't expect that (MND
OL,9,Fdiagnosis)," he said.
OL,11,F"That was it really, they gave me a
OL,12,Fleaflet and off I went. I went on my
OL,13,Fown because I just said to my wife, I
OL,14,Fdon't need you here really. I can deal
OL,15,Fwith this. Not expecting it to be MND.
OL,17,F"The first week's quite tough because
OL,18,Fyou're thinking about what's
OL,19,Fhappening, you're thinking about doing
OL,20,Fa will, which is the strangest thing.
