OL,6,F"It's then onto how do you tell family
OL,7,Fmembers, which was the toughest thing
OL,8,Fto do."
OL,10,FBut he added: "I must have had 2,000
OL,11,Femails, texts, whatsapps and phone
OL,12,Fcalls in the first five days from
OL,13,Fbeing diagnosed."
OL,15,FStewart got in touch with fellow
OL,16,Fformer footballer Stephen Darby, who
OL,17,Fplayed nearly 200 games for Bradford
OL,18,FCity before developing MND.
