OL,6,FThe pair will be joined by more than
OL,7,F600 walkers on 22 March on their
OL,8,F"March of the Day" from to Bolton,
OL,9,Fdressed in the blue of .
OL,11,FVisiting 17 stadiums over the next
OL,12,Fcouple of days, the group will then
OL,13,Fdon the red shirts of Darby's boyhood
OL,14,Fclub Liverpool, before finishing at
OL,15,FAnfield on 24 March.
OL,17,FHe added: "I've got a new set of
OL,18,Fteammates in the MND community. Rob
OL,19,F(Burrow), Kev (Sinfield) and Stephen
OL,20,FDarby are up there being captain,
OL,21,Fmanager and leading the way.
