OL,6,F"I've got a different set of teammates
OL,7,Fnow. And the old ones are still
OL,8,Fsupporting me, which I love.
OL,10,F"It will be nice for the football
OL,11,Fcommunity to show their support in
OL,12,Fsome way."
OL,14,FOn fellow MND fundraiser Rob Burrow,
OL,15,Fhe said: "We're a bit like Rob's house
OL,16,FI suppose. It's a no crying house. Not
OL,17,Fbecause we don't want to, but I don't
OL,18,Fthink we have time because we're
OL,19,Falways organising something.
